::: Marine, tired, and hurt from the battle rose up. He grabbed his missle 
launcer and made his way towrds Shuko. He was shot, of course, but didnt care 
anymore. He picked up the tyrant, and dug his missle launcher into the 
smaller bots throat. :::

::: Marine ::: Call of your attack now, or I will kill you.

::: Just to get his point across, Marine used his one good optic laser and 
shot it at Shuko's stomach, still gripping his neck so he wouldnt slip 
away. :::
